Title: Love in Africa
DateModified: '2019-03-06'
DatePublished: '2019-03-06'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/love-in-africa
SetInCountry: South Africa
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Theo Lebese
AuthorCountry: South Africa
Text: "A love story of an American Boy meets an African girl in the south who takes\
  \ him on a journey he's never been in,a journey of culture\n\nA breath of the fresh\
  \ air \n\nThe boy falls in love with the girl but unfortunately he has to go back\
  \ to his country but never stops thinking about the girl as he grows up in his country\n\
  \nHe ends up going back ,a couple of years later to look for the girl and finds\
  \ her,together they move to his country and live happily ever after"
